How To Record Any Device Without A Capture Card!

What You Will Need:

A Device (Hdmi)
Xbox One
A PC
The Xbox App (PC)

Step One (Connections)

1. Plug The Device Hdmi Port (The One You Want To Record With) Into The Hdmi In Port Of The Xbox
2. Make Sure That Device Is On (Tne One You Want To Record With)

Step Two (Xbox)

1. Turn On The Xbox
2. Open The TV App On Your Xbox
(If The Device Is On, It Will Show Your Device Screen)

Step Three (PC)

1. Open The Xbox App On Your Pc
2. Go To Connect And Connect To Your Xbox
(If You Did It, You Will See Your Xbox Screen (Or If You Have The TV App Open, Then The Device))

That Is It
